            <title><![CDATA[简悦为什么使用 Revue 作为 Newsletter 的平台]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p dir="auto"><a href="https://imgchr.com/i/yNZMrQ" rel="nofollow"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/9aec14ca548e0528b6ee5e48588f715bcf9872402c24caf56a80e63f9129f695/68747470733a2f2f73332e617831782e636f6d2f323032312f30322f30372f794e5a4d72512e706e67" alt="yNZMrQ.png" data-canonical-src="https://s3.ax1x.com/2021/02/07/yNZMrQ.png" style="max-width: 100%;"></a></p>
<blockquote>
<p dir="auto">简悦想用 Newsletter 好久了，一直没有适合的平台，今天无意中发现了 <a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.getrevue.co/" rel="nofollow">revue</a> 这是一个被 Twitter 收购的 Newsletter 平台，我准备将 简悦的 Newsletter 放到这里。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 dir="auto">订阅</h2>
<blockquote>
<p dir="auto">嗨，如果你喜欢 <a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//twitter.com/hashtag/%E7%AE%80%E6%82%A6%3Fsrc%3Dhashtag_click" rel="nofollow">#简悦</a> 或 生产力工具 / 工作流 的 Newsletter 爱好者，可以订阅我的这份简报</p>
</blockquote>
<p dir="auto"><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.getrevue.co/profile/kenshin" rel="nofollow">https://www.getrevue.co/profile/kenshinwww.getrevue.co</a></p>
<h2 dir="auto">负一期</h2>
<blockquote>
<p dir="auto">这篇文章是通过此平台撰写的第「负一期」<br>
至于为什么是负一期，因为本篇文章是 <strong>测试版</strong>，用来测试此平台的效果 <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="grin" fallback-src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f601.png">😁</g-emoji></p>
</blockquote>
<p dir="auto"><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.getrevue.co/profile/kenshin/issues/weekly-newsletter-of-kenshin-1-353216" rel="nofollow">https://www.getrevue.co/profile/kenshin/issues/weekly-newsletter-of-kenshin-1-353216www.getrevue.co</a></p>
<hr>
<blockquote>
<p dir="auto">以下是 Revue 的一些介绍。</p>
</blockquote>
<h2 dir="auto">背景介绍</h2>
<p dir="auto"><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//t.co/trVgZPvOFM%3Famp%3D1" rel="nofollow">https://getrevue.co</a> 是 Twitter 刚刚收购的 Newsletter 平台，我没有用过其它平台，仅聊聊「我为什么使用 Revue 作为 Newsletter 的平台」</p>
<p dir="auto">在 Twitter 收购 Revue 后，整合 Twitter 到 Revue 中（ 可以使用推的帐号直接登录 Revue） 同时在登录到 Revue 后，你会发现可以在其中嵌入推文 结合 Threaded Twitter 的写作方式，你可以将这些信息方便的「导入到」 Newsletter</p>
<p dir="auto"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/6917702633482a7c658c087bf8a346feb0f8c437337efbf07774e1f07b78b2a0/68747470733a2f2f706963332e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d33643666623661613465656239626230373965373262636366663831313563615f373230772e6a7067"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/6917702633482a7c658c087bf8a346feb0f8c437337efbf07774e1f07b78b2a0/68747470733a2f2f706963332e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d33643666623661613465656239626230373965373262636366663831313563615f373230772e6a7067" alt="img" data-canonical-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-3d6fb6aa4eeb9bb079e72bccff8115ca_720w.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;"></a></p>
<p dir="auto">这还不是唯一导入方式。</p>
<h2 dir="auto">Revue 还支持多种导入方式</h2>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>
<p dir="auto">常规工具，如： Pocket，Instapaper，Medium 甚至 RSS 也可以</p>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">提供浏览器插件。</p>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">甚至于可以接入 Zapier 平台<a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//t.co/djIokZhLvB%3Famp%3D1" rel="nofollow">https://getrevue.co/app/integrations/zapier</a></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p dir="auto"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/1f7f61597484bda5486f5eca37226fa2fa74d236d903baefb7feccefdaac98d8/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d35366366656266386234656464663866346339616337336437393930663266645f373230772e6a7067"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/1f7f61597484bda5486f5eca37226fa2fa74d236d903baefb7feccefdaac98d8/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d35366366656266386234656464663866346339616337336437393930663266645f373230772e6a7067" alt="img" data-canonical-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-56cfebf8b4eddf8f4c9ac73d7990f2fd_720w.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;"></a></p>
<p dir="auto"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/aec54e84ffc49e91451f6c210beaf497c1c19c9fb39f21c7697b08ca57aa41e6/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d62623666343864663530343464393063363138663562343630323231626135645f373230772e6a7067"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/aec54e84ffc49e91451f6c210beaf497c1c19c9fb39f21c7697b08ca57aa41e6/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d62623666343864663530343464393063363138663562343630323231626135645f373230772e6a7067" alt="img" data-canonical-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-bb6f48df5044d90c618f5b460221ba5d_720w.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;"></a></p>
<p dir="auto">通过（上面）这些功能，你可以将发到推或 Pocket / Medium 之类的内容方便的通过拖拽即可生成一篇 Newsletter 本篇文章 <a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//t.co/X2i7R9USed%3Famp%3D1" rel="nofollow">https://getrevue.co/profile/kenshin/issues/weekly-newsletter-of-kenshin-1-353216…</a> 就是通过此产生的。</p>
<p dir="auto">从构思到完成，花费我不一个小时的时间。（包括第一次使用时的入门时间，如果单说内容时间，绝对不超过二十分钟）</p>
<h2 dir="auto">再谈谈编辑环境</h2>
<p dir="auto">除了上面说的拖拽方案外，还支持类似 Medium 的写作方案，包括：拖拽排序，图文混排，提供 H1 文本 超链接以及文字内样式。 同时支持一定程度的「带有样式的粘贴」方式。</p>
<p dir="auto"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/9889daca8ff291754bd7d1384e94db5dae22a559cae08d28c698305f5c0ee74b/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d37633238306538323839653661646535666233386539623032303639363965395f373230772e6a7067"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/9889daca8ff291754bd7d1384e94db5dae22a559cae08d28c698305f5c0ee74b/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d37633238306538323839653661646535666233386539623032303639363965395f373230772e6a7067" alt="img" data-canonical-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-7c280e8289e6ade5fb38e9b0206969e9_720w.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;"></a></p>
<p dir="auto"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/cbe3db5ca1c2793366b2d7b0f09d01bee3da9658b6ae03e6f385a7d8695a2553/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d33633761633663653332623336336465633932663238306236666264333037315f373230772e6a7067"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/cbe3db5ca1c2793366b2d7b0f09d01bee3da9658b6ae03e6f385a7d8695a2553/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d33633761633663653332623336336465633932663238306236666264333037315f373230772e6a7067" alt="img" data-canonical-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-3c7ac6ce32b363dec92f280b6fbd3071_720w.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;"></a></p>
<p dir="auto"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/afee855a56cc3deeb0aba2669e7e6fec53c0e13e12f8eb9a424866f7ce62758d/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d32343133366532343134333235306262373964343032643564376134346537395f373230772e6a7067"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/afee855a56cc3deeb0aba2669e7e6fec53c0e13e12f8eb9a424866f7ce62758d/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d32343133366532343134333235306262373964343032643564376134346537395f373230772e6a7067" alt="img" data-canonical-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-24136e24143250bb79d402d5d7a44e79_720w.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;"></a></p>
<h2 dir="auto">订阅的渠道</h2>
<p dir="auto">基本上涵盖了常见的场景，如 Import from Mailchimp， Import from file 等方式。</p>
<p dir="auto"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d24a40a25c043ef32cd2163d334db403a536883cf2641e0a79bbc81a61d3e0df/68747470733a2f2f706963332e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d66363262343433376533316432396233626136313561616431393366373539615f373230772e6a7067"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/d24a40a25c043ef32cd2163d334db403a536883cf2641e0a79bbc81a61d3e0df/68747470733a2f2f706963332e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d66363262343433376533316432396233626136313561616431393366373539615f373230772e6a7067" alt="img" data-canonical-src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-f62b4437e31d29b3ba615aad193f759a_720w.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;"></a></p>
