<p dir="auto"><a href="https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//t.co/Z1cVKz8e1g%3Famp%3D1" rel="nofollow">https://getrevue.co/api</a> 包含常见的一些使用场景，如果有编程能力的话，很容易将 Revue 嵌入到你的程序中。</p>
<p dir="auto"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/1468806d7ce18ac8fc297e82fde39b77a9add058f1b2934c40dc74c032635ddc/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d39613261383338633638366338336537626431363262626265343965366463395f373230772e6a7067"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/1468806d7ce18ac8fc297e82fde39b77a9add058f1b2934c40dc74c032635ddc/68747470733a2f2f706963322e7a68696d672e636f6d2f38302f76322d39613261383338633638366338336537626431363262626265343965366463395f373230772e6a7067" alt="img" data-canonical-src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-9a2a838c686c83e7bd162bbbe49e6dc9_720w.jpg" style="max-width: 100%;"></a></p>
