<li><a href="https://twitter.com/wanglei001/status/1358322013492948992" rel="nofollow">https://twitter.com/wanglei001/status/1358322013492948992</a></li>
<li><a href="https://threadreaderapp.com/thread/1358322013492948992.html" rel="nofollow">https://threadreaderapp.com/thread/1358322013492948992.html</a></li>
</ul>
<h2 dir="auto">近期一些技巧汇总</h2>
<ol dir="auto">
<li>
<p dir="auto">如何利用简悦 · 同步助手快速回源原页面的任意位置 <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="point_right" fallback-src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f449.png">👉</g-emoji> <a href="https://github.com/Kenshin/simpread/discussions/1720">https://github.com/Kenshin/simpread/discussions/1720</a><br>
来自社区用户 <a href="https://t.me/BONABC" rel="nofollow">@BONABC</a> 的技巧</p>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">在 Mac 端导出 PDF 出现二次编辑错位情况的解决方案（Windows 用户无此问题） <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="point_right" fallback-src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f449.png">👉</g-emoji> <a href="https://github.com/Kenshin/simpread/discussions/1772">https://github.com/Kenshin/simpread/discussions/1772</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">关于 Notion 无法授权或导入空文件等问题的集中说明（附解决方案） <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="point_right" fallback-src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f449.png">👉</g-emoji> <a href="https://github.com/Kenshin/simpread/discussions/1773">https://github.com/Kenshin/simpread/discussions/1773</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">一定要小心「数据孤岛」,一旦形成后就没法迁移 <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="point_right" fallback-src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f449.png">👉</g-emoji> <a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/348520757" rel="nofollow">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/348520757</a></p>
</li>
<li>
<p dir="auto">如何在稍后读内置的阅读模式中导出含有标注的全文（仅限 HTML） <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="point_right" fallback-src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f449.png">👉</g-emoji>  <a href="https://github.com/Kenshin/simpread/discussions/1712">https://github.com/Kenshin/simpread/discussions/1712</a></p>
</li>
</ol>
<blockquote>
<p dir="auto">我会在每周发一个【简悦技巧汇总】，如果你也喜欢订阅 RSS 的话，订阅地址 <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="point_right" fallback-src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f449.png">👉</g-emoji> <a href="https://rss.simpread.pro/feed" rel="nofollow">https://rss.simpread.pro/feed</a> 以及其它简悦的 RSS 订阅源 <g-emoji class="g-emoji" alias="point_right" fallback-src="https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f449.png">👉</g-emoji> <a href="https://simpread.pro/subscribe" rel="nofollow">https://simpread.pro/subscribe</a></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 dir="auto">Clubhouse</h2>
